@startuml UC20_Sequence
title UC20: 审核成绩 - 顺序图

actor "管理员" as Admin
boundary "审核门户" as Portal
control "审核控制器" as AuditCtrl
entity "Grade" as Grade

Admin -> Portal : 查看待审成绩并提交意见
Portal -> AuditCtrl : auditGrades(gradeIds, action)
loop 每个成绩
    AuditCtrl -> Grade : setAuditStatus(action)
    Grade --> AuditCtrl : updated
end
AuditCtrl --> Portal : 审批完成提示
@enduml
